# RPC admin password file.
#
# `service/network/rpc/rpc_server.rs::load_or_create_admin_password`
# writes this file on first run as a convenience for the operator
# (the canonical password is stored in RocksDB at key
# `rpc:admin_password`). It MUST NEVER be committed: doing so
# publishes the live admin credential for any node that ever ran
# from this checkout.
rpc_password
target/ 
.claude/ 
